text: The 1968 Kensington and Chelsea Council election took place on 9 May 1968 to elect members of Kensington and Chelsea London Borough Council in London, England. The whole council was up for election and the Conservative party stayed in overall control of the council. ==Background== ==Election result== ==Ward results== ==References== 1968 Category:1968 London Borough council elections Category:20th century in the Royal Borough of Kensington and Chelsea
title: 1968 Kensington and Chelsea London Borough Council election
